      "bookmarkId": "40666978_8_526-540",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "526-540",
      "markText": "犹太人是历史上最顽强的民族。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=526&rangeEnd=540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=526&rangeEnd=540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_7_1809-1825",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1809-1825",
      "markText": "历史自有其目的，人类自有其命运。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_5_749-792",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "749-792",
      "markText": "在经历了1800余年的大流散之后，犹太人为何依然能够保持民族特性，没有被寄居国所同化？",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=749&rangeEnd=792",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=749&rangeEnd=792"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_7_1693-1782",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1693-1782",
      "markText": "我们究竟为何存在？历史仅仅是一连串加在一起毫无意义的事件吗？人类的历史与蚂蚁的历史在道德上是否没什么根本差别？或者，是否存在一个天定的计划，而我们人类是这个计划足够谦卑的代理人？",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1693&rangeEnd=1782",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1693&rangeEnd=1782"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_7_2006-2037",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2006-2037",
      "markText": "在给人类以有尊严、有意义的生活的长期努力中，犹太人是中流砥柱。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2006&rangeEnd=2037",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2006&rangeEnd=2037"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_8_2578-2614",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2578-2614",
      "markText": "他们已经无可挽回地消失在时间的长河里。但是，犹太人还在希伯伦，依旧如故。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2578&rangeEnd=2614",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2578&rangeEnd=2614"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_5_575-612",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "575-612",
      "markText": "在电影和纪录片中，许多人看到过第二次世界大战期间纳粹对犹太人的迫害和屠杀。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_15_75852-75894",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "75852-75894",
      "markText": "在反犹最激烈的沙皇亚历山大三世诞辰那天，全巴黎的犹太会堂都举行专门的祷告会为他祈福，",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=75852&rangeEnd=75894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=75852&rangeEnd=75894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_7_1131-1212",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1131-1212",
      "markText": "这种非凡的忍耐力源自何处？让犹太人与众不同并保持为同一类人的那种强烈信念的特殊力量是什么？这个民族的延续能力是由于它的一成不变，还是它的适应能力，或者两种均有呢？",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1131&rangeEnd=1212",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1131&rangeEnd=1212"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_5_2691-2764",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2691-2764",
      "markText": "保罗·约翰逊认为，从那些受苦受难的犹太人的视角来看待世界历史上的重大事件，能够为历史增添新的内容，使犹太人作为受压迫者的历史真实地呈现在人们面前。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2691&rangeEnd=2764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2691&rangeEnd=2764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_7_1070-1107",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1070-1107",
      "markText": "与几乎所有现存的其他民族相比，犹太人更早地形成了具体且有区分性的身份认同。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1070&rangeEnd=1107",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1070&rangeEnd=1107"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_8_2699-2784",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2699-2784",
      "markText": "没有哪个民族能够在如此漫长的岁月里对大地上的某个特定角落在情感上保持如此强烈的依恋，也没有哪个民族能够表现出如此强烈而执着的迁徙本能以及将自己连根拔起并移栽的勇气和本领。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2699&rangeEnd=2784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2699&rangeEnd=2784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_8_52347-52385",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "52347-52385",
      "markText": "以色列人的征服过程弥漫着绝望的情绪，这就解释了他们在占领城池后为何如此残酷。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=52347&rangeEnd=52385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=52347&rangeEnd=52385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_5_2049-2093",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2049-2093",
      "markText": "德国在中世纪就有如此浓厚的反犹传统，因而不难理解为何纳粹德国时期会发生惨绝人寰的大屠杀。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2049&rangeEnd=2093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2049&rangeEnd=2093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40666978_5_1925-1966",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1925-1966",
      "markText": "反犹主义在中世纪晚期的德国尤为严重，这一时期的德国开始用一种母猪的图形代表犹太人。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40666978&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1925&rangeEnd=1966",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/910323a0726c87629106646?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1925&rangeEnd=1966"
